    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An open file format standard for electronic document exchange via the Internet. Developed by Adobe Systems to encode the visual representation of a document independent of the type of software used to write or read it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
